name: New Startpage - SGL 3.0 (AIR)
description: This is the style you're looking for. SGL 2.0 (Classic) has been revived for Startpage's new design. Now comes with enhanced video and upgraded image results. No ads, static header, images embedded for enhanced privacy.
additional_info: UPDATE 06/24/15: Special Thanks to Jonathan Salmon for porting SGL 2.0 (Classic) to startpage's new design! ______________________________________________ FYI: Either disable SGL 2.0 & 3.0 (Classic) themes, OR alter their domains to classic.startpage.com before using this style which is for startpage.com. ______________________________________________ BENEFIT TO USERS: It looks just like the classic, yet has new and improved video/image search functionality.
